1. Čujem* da ćeš uskoro biti roditelj. (I hear that you will soon become a parent.)

2. Čula* sam da je ovaj film dobar. (I heard that this movie is good.)

3. Čuješ* li mene? (Do you hear me?)

4. Čuli* smo o njegovom uspehu. (We heard about his success.)

5. Čuješ* li buku? (Do you hear the noise?)

6. Čujemo* te jasno. (We hear you clearly.)